rce and effect upon termination or expiration of the agreement.\n\n**Rights and Obligations:**\n\n* The Fund bears all costs and expenses incurred in its operation, administration, and transactions, except for those specifically assumed by the Adviser pursuant to the Advisory Agreement or this Agreement.\n* The Blockchain Administrator will provide services related to the development of ERC-1404 compatible digital securities and administration of the smart contracts underlying the Fund's digital securities.\n* The Blockchain Administrator will serve as the Fund's investment adviser pursuant to an Investment Advisory Agreement.\n\n**Definitions:**\n\n* \"Blockchain Administrator\" refers to ARCA CAPITAL MANAGEMENT, LLC.\n* \"Fund\" refers to ARCA U.S. TREASURY FUND.\n* \"Adviser\" refers to the Blockchain Administrator in its capacity as the Fund's investment adviser.\n* \"Advisory Agreement\" refers to the Investment Advisory Agreement entered into by and between the Fund and the Adviser.\n* \"Investment Company Act\" refers to the Investment Company Act of 1940, as amended.\n* \"Investment Fund Act\" refers to the applicable provisions of the Investment Fund Act.",
