he Documentation), pursuant to the Project specifications detailed in the SO (collectively, Specifications), as described in the enclosed statement of work (the SOW\u037e as provided in APPENDIX A hereto). The Parties may execute multiple SOWs should there be multiple or separate Projects.\n",
